# Copyable Paths and URLs

## In tables and inline text

Wrap file paths and URLs in backticks for easy selection:

| # | Type | Link |
|---|------|------|
| 1 | URL | `https://example.com/path` |
| 2 | File | `/home/user/project/file.rs` |

